  <p class="manifesto" id="manifesto">
    AI can generate anything now. That's exactly the problem. Outbuild Lab
    is built on the other half — the taste to know what's worth building,
    and the judgment to make AI ship it at production quality. The model is
    our medium. The decisions are the work.
  </p>

